@* The static consumer of CascadeTwoConsumers.razor's cascade -- the sibling child composition
   resolves. Identical to Unsupported/Gate/GaugeA.razor: a child is resolved as a SAME-DIRECTORY
   .razor, so the control needs its own copy beside the parent that composes it. *@
<span id="a">@Level</span>

@code {
    [Parameter] public string Tag { get; set; } = "";
